# mini-saas-api — editor-runnable requests (VS Code REST Client / JetBrains).
# Run the server first: go run .  (default :8090)

@base = http://localhost:8090
@access = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refresh = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

### Liveness
GET {{base}}/healthz

### Readiness
GET {{base}}/readyz

### Sign up: creates user + workspace, returns token pair
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "name": "Alice",
  "password": "Str0ng!Password#2026",
  "workspace_name": "Acme",
  "workspace_slug": "acme"
}

### Log in (optionally pass "workspace_slug" to pick a workspace)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Password#2026"
}

### Rotate the refresh token (single-use; reuse revokes the session family)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refresh}}"
}

### Current principal
GET {{base}}/api/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Workspace details + project usage
GET {{base}}/api/v1/tenant
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Rename workspace (admin+)
PATCH {{base}}/api/v1/tenant
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Acme Renamed" }

### List members
GET {{base}}/api/v1/tenant/members
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Add member by email (admin+; the account must exist)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/tenant/members
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "bob@example.com", "role": "member" }

### Change member role (admin+; cannot demote the last owner)
PATCH {{base}}/api/v1/tenant/members/MEMBERSHIP_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "admin" }

### Remove member (admin+; cannot remove the last owner)
DELETE {{base}}/api/v1/tenant/members/MEMBERSHIP_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Audit trail, newest first (admin+)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/tenant/audit?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### List projects
GET {{base}}/api/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Create project — Idempotency-Key makes retries safe
POST {{base}}/api/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: create-apollo-1

{ "name": "Apollo", "description": "first project" }

### Get one project
GET {{base}}/api/v1/projects/PROJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Update project (status: active | paused | archived)
PUT {{base}}/api/v1/projects/PROJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Apollo 11", "status": "paused" }

### Delete project (admin+)
DELETE {{base}}/api/v1/projects/PROJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Prometheus metrics (Bearer APP_METRICS_TOKEN when configured)
GET {{base}}/metrics
